cs.SE, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.SY, cs.PL 

The paper discusses the need for better tools for software engineers to make use of AI software, specifically for software defect prediction and software text mining. This falls under the category of software engineering (cs.SE) and machine learning (cs.LG, cs.AI). The paper also discusses hyperparameter optimization, which is a common topic in systems and control (cs.SY) and programming languages (cs.PL) as it relates to optimizing the performance of software systems.
